Title: Sketchy Nonsense Live Podcast 2: We're Doing It Again
Presenters: Shane Soules, Andy Althouse, Nick Haynes, Anne LaCroix
Book Description: Sketchy Nonsense is back again to do our patented (not actually patented) live podcast! Come see a group of guys do some live improv comedy for your listening pleasure. And also drink beer. And ALSO also- you can drink it with us! Sample the 'Beer of the Week' with us. It is most definitely 21+- so bring your big boy/girl/non-gender conforming pants and have a fun time! This event is 18+.

Title: Spooky Stories with Marshmallows on Top
Book Description: I'll bring the hot cocoa- you bring your real-life spooky- creepy or just strange paranormal stories. An open mind is encouraged- but you're welcome to think we're all weirdos and just enjoy cocoa and storytime. Join us as we share some personal 'no s*it- there I was' experiences. An event to savor. (Marshmallows and sharing optional.) This event is 18+.
